Common patterns:

### State

 - `%‌{‌state.title‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌state.description‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌state.language‌}‌%`
 - …

### Time

 - `%‌{‌time.year‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌time.month‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌time.en‌}‌%`
 - …

### Page

 - `%‌{‌page.url‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌page.title‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌page.description‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌page.link‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌page.author‌}‌%`
 - …

### Site

 - `%‌{‌site.title‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌site.description‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌site.page.title‌}‌%`
 - `%‌{‌site.page.description‌}‌%`
 - …

### URL

 - `%‌{‌url‌}‌%` → `http://127.0.0.1/a`
 - `%‌{‌url.protocol‌}‌%` → `http://`
 - `%‌{‌url.host‌}‌%` → `127.0.0.1`
 - `%‌{‌url.port‌}‌%` → `80`
 - `%‌{‌url.d‌}‌%` → `/a`
 - `%‌{‌url.path‌}‌%` → `/foo/bar`
 - `%‌{‌url.query‌}‌%` → `?foo=bar&baz=qux`
 - `%‌{‌url.current‌}‌%` → `http://127.0.0.1/a/foo/bar?foo=bar&baz=qux`

