### Custom

Add your custom syntax or replace the default syntax in the `v` property, remove the default syntax in `x`:

~~~ .php
[
    'v' => [
        'asset' => 'http://127.0.0.1/lot/asset'
        …
    ],
    'x' => [ … ]
]
~~~